GBC Web Design Intent
===============================
Main Goal:  Convert the "Sample App" into "GBC Web App"

1. The home page should have a news feed.  The news feed gets updated
   based on what an administrator posts.  Therefore we will need to implement
   a news model. (Implemented, just need to clean up)

2. Clean up the user model and remove the sample data from the database.  Also consider
   removing the relationship model and table in the database.
